window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A witch on the run who could save the world–or destroy it with one touch.</p> <p>I am who they fear.</p> <p>The Harvester Death Witch.</p> <p>The one who holds the power of their fate in my hands.</p> <p>Or at least...that’s what they whisper.</p> <p>The coven has fallen. The vampires are circling our den. And if we don’t find new allies, our Pack won’t be able to fight much longer.</p> <p>On my Alpha’s orders, I must find others who hide beneath the shadows for not only our protection, but theirs as well.</p> <p>Only I’m not alone on my mission.</p> <p>I brought Cruz back from death once before, and though I know the goddess forbids it, I’d do it again.</p> <p>Because he’s my mate.</p> <p>And my ending.</p>"; 
